summary: The human version of the Argonian Race
descriptionHtml:
Here is an alternate version to the Argonian Race. If you don't like playing lizards then this is your Argonian race! It is an exact copy of an Argonian except for the look of the character, more human.

Disclaimer: Any images shown are purely cosmetic mods that I have installed, and are the owners of the displayed mods. I take no credit for any cosmetics added to my images with the mods I use to play the game. If you have a vanilla setup you can still play the races
author: michael2mandy
